n war, doing minute damge and getting all exp.  The bards had to actually kill evey mob, the charmers actually had their pet attack other mobs, not set off a chain reaction of events that they keep feeding to gather exp.  The 2 examples you listed are normal exp methods gotten out of hand.  This is not a normal exp method.  You shouldn't get any exp at all for this tactic.  It's an exploit, plain and simple.</span id="msg"></font></td>
